Protestant Scholasticism or Aristotelianism.
Scholasticism经院哲学Aristotelianism（与）亚里士多德（有关）的哲学
Kopfreligion, head religion.

We shall know the Lord, and we shall love the Lord. We shall not preach knowledge along, but with the passion and love. We shall have both the head and passion.

Herzreligion, breast religion.

Pietism based on our emotion rather than the truth of scripture. This is the crisis of theology, because the base is emotion, which is a weak thing.

Modernism stress on intelligence and logic, postmodernism stress on emotion and will.

The second crisis of theology is the tendency to put theology in the area of humanities.

The third crisis of theology is the age of the post truth area.

The fourth crisis of theology is the tendency of escaping from the church group.

The fifth crisis of theology is the attention of human not on belief but on life.

The sixth crisis of theology is that we think personal faith is more important than public confession.

The seventh crisis of theology is the emergence of today’s life.

According to Aristoteles, all knowledge can be divided into three areas: Physics to describe moving objects, Mathematics to describe numbers, Theology to describe unmoving objects.

Physics inside space and time, it’s logos, theology is above the space and time, it’s mythos. Yeah, He is all the base, all the rules.

Theology is the prima philosophia(primary philosophy).

According to Anselmus, theology means “faith seeking understanding”.

We show know others first, than be friends with each other. But I think we should be friends with each other, than get to know each other, and our professor admitted such order in our religion, that we must believe Him first, and than get to know Him more.

Cosmos-Theology, use the final cause to prove the existence of God. All existence has cause, the final one has no cause, that’s God.

Ontological theology, if there is God, there are some properties of God, such as omnipresent, or eternal life, so there is God. Although something are beautiful in our eyes, it can be ugly in others’ eyes.

The sacrifice of Jesus Christ, satisfied the RIGHTEOUSNESS and LOVE of God.

Two light source, Lumen Naturae, Lumen Gratiae, light of nature, light of grace. The general revelation, and the special revelation. The latter one is the Bible.

Catholic is the captivity of Babylon, the reformation is the deliverance of the elected people, said Martin Luther.

Calvin said, “Only Bible”, different with Luther, he admitted the intelligence of humanity, Luther thinks the intelligence as prostitute, we should kill the biggest enemy of God, the intelligence. But Calvin thinks we should use the intelligence of reborn intelligence.

Schleiermacher divided the areas of theology, such as practical theology, and theoretical theology. He thinks the whole theological knowledge as an organism, a systematical body.

There are 4 types of theology, biblical theology, theoretical theology, historical theology, and practical theology. Some other types included in above 4 types.

The Theology of Pilgrims is imperfect, the Theology of the Blessed is a more full, clear, deeper, and complete understanding.






